## Note on Odd Dimensions

VMD renders may not always produce images with dimensions divisible by 32
(YOLO's preferred stride). FFmpeg's `-1` flag handles this automatically,
but if you see a warning, force even height:

```bash
# Force height to nearest even number (safe for all codecs)
ffmpeg -i input.png -vf scale=384:-2 output.png
```

